    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.poster.avif?t=1768793701\" width=620 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.webm?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/2dc7e7cbf2147ddf6f1c8d86110efaaa.mp4?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/b5308b0a03f40ee804012e1800c5300e.poster.avif?t=1768793701\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/b5308b0a03f40ee804012e1800c5300e.webm?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/b5308b0a03f40ee804012e1800c5300e.mp4?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/13e56188fb148916beb1648c22973c32.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><br>你是神秘沙漠星球恩索拉的殖民者的后裔。与地球失去联系后，人们分成几组，为剩余的食物和资源进行了绝望的斗争。你能反击野蛮的暴徒吗？你会发现强大公司的秘密吗？你有机会回家吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/9b0938cf61e76fd5b263643f661193b4.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><br>在游戏中，你必须面对很多快速的战斗。战斗的结果通常取决于玩家的速度和准确性。要获胜，请使用所有可用的武器——从能量步枪到战斗导弹。提高你的技能，变得无敌！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/a7fcbcf9df6aef4ecb6990663f52146c.poster.avif?t=1768793701\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/a7fcbcf9df6aef4ecb6990663f52146c.webm?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/a7fcbcf9df6aef4ecb6990663f52146c.mp4?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/c97c26f6bdb4e2acf821ad8a2f504e30.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><br>要探索这个星球，你必须控制一艘宇宙飞船。在船上，您可以监控燃料水平和食物、贸易或工艺有用物品的数量。休息会恢复你的健康。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/43bfc9c6913d0b680b33e00b73d0d4dc.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=230 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/3d166e1bae7306603880c1565c91913a.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><br>当你离开飞船寻找食物和资源时，你会遇到恩索拉的许多危险——野生生物、土匪、机器人等等。请记住，障碍重重的道路往往会带来最丰厚的回报。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/37c24726fa0bbe5f21317094ad1ea6ee.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=203 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/ebb894b9b45145e003c079be1e5c3f46.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><br>从隐藏在游戏地点的书籍、秘密著作或信件中了解恩索拉殖民者和强大公司的历史。利用您对恩索拉历史的了解，解开传送门之谜并返回地球。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/ac722b8e7c73d61cb912b55b2ca6dccb.poster.avif?t=1768793701\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/ac722b8e7c73d61cb912b55b2ca6dccb.webm?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/ac722b8e7c73d61cb912b55b2ca6dccb.mp4?t=1768793701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112210/extras/b8e21c7ad92b66d3c1e12d2de03da3d1.avif?t=1768793701\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在探索游戏地图的同时控制宇宙飞船<br></li><li>制作武器和弹药来对抗你的敌人<br></li><li>寻找、购买或窃取食物和其他有价值的资源<br></li><li>骑着未来派的自行车穿越地球的无边无际<br></li><li>破解公司的安全系统以到达隐藏的地方和高价值物品<br></li><li>升级舰船系统、装甲、武器等</li></ul>",
